#: /home/h-kuroki/work/drbd-doc-ja/proto/v9/base/adoc/linstor-cloudstack.adoc:204
msgid ""
"350 is the `max_connections` value specified in http://docs.cloudstack.apache.org/en/latest/quickinstallationguide/qig.html#database-installation-and-configuration[the "
"CloudStack installation guide]. You can change this value depending on your needs."
