#. type: Plain text
#: /home/h-kuroki/work/drbd-doc-ja/proto/v9/base/adoc/linstor-cloudstack.adoc:317
msgid ""
"CloudStack needs to run some system VMs for some of its functionality. You can download a CloudStack VM template image and then run a CloudStack script that will prepare "
"the image for various system VMs in deployment. On the CloudStack management node, enter the following commands:"
msgstr ""
"CloudStackは、機能の一部のためにシステムVMをいくつか実行する必要があります。CloudStack VMテンプレートイメージをダウンロードし、その後CloudStackスクリプトを実行して、展開され"
"るさまざまなシステムVMに必要なイメージを準備します。CloudStack管理ノードで以下のコマンドを入力してください。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: /home/h-kuroki/work/drbd-doc-ja/proto/v9/base/adoc/linstor-cloudstack.adoc:326
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# CS_VERSION=4.17\n"
"# CS_VERSION_PATCH=4.17.1\n"
"# wget https://download.cloudstack.org/systemvm/$CS_VERSION/systemvmtemplate-$CS_VERSION_PATCH-kvm.qcow2.bz2\n"
"# /usr/share/cloudstack-common/scripts/storage/secondary/cloud-install-sys-tmplt \\\n"
"-m /export/secondary \\\n"
"-f systemvmtemplate-$CS_VERSION_PATCH=-kvm.qcow2.bz2 \\\n"
"-h kvm -o localhost -r cloud -d cloud\n"
msgstr ""
"# CS_VERSION=4.17\n"
"# CS_VERSION_PATCH=4.17.1\n"
"# wget https://download.cloudstack.org/systemvm/$CS_VERSION/systemvmtemplate-$CS_VERSION_PATCH-kvm.qcow2.bz2\n"
"# /usr/share/cloudstack-common/scripts/storage/secondary/cloud-install-sys-tmplt \\\n"
"-m /export/secondary \\\n"
"-f systemvmtemplate-$CS_VERSION_PATCH=-kvm.qcow2.bz2 \\\n"
"-h kvm -o localhost -r cloud -d cloud\n"

#. type: Title ===
#: /home/h-kuroki/work/drbd-doc-ja/proto/v9/base/adoc/linstor-cloudstack.adoc:329
#, no-wrap
msgid "Configuring KVM Hypervisor Hosts for Use in CloudStack"
