#: /home/h-kuroki/work/drbd-doc-ja/proto/v9/base/adoc/linstor-cloudstack.adoc:384
msgid ""
"After some time, you should be able to log in to the CloudStack management UI. Given a management node resolvable hostname of `node-0`, enter the following URL into a web "
